{"type": "article", "id": 31422, "title": "Kate Spade做可穿戴，以及，Calvin Klein秋冬针织还不错 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-08-25T02:20:52Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 27500, "name": "wisdom"}, {"id": 31954, "name": ":CHOCOOLATE"}, {"id": 325, "name": "Fendi"}, {"id": 1066, "name": "Calvin Klein"}, {"id": 2816, "name": "Kate Spade"}, {"id": 3865, "name": "adidas Originals"}, {"id": 4949, "name": "Guess"}, {"id": 976, "name": "Rihanna"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 38, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160825083813ByzaOCtsn0i71oGM.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/calvin-klein-leads-pvh-second-quarter-sales-higher-10514658/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Calvin Klein 推动 PVH 集团第二季度收入增长</b></a> | 作为全球第二大服装集团，PVH 截止至 7 月 31 日的三个月收入从 18.6 亿美元增长至 19.3 亿美元。由于在北美市场表现不错，该集团旗下的 Calvin Klein 第二季度收入增长了 12%，至 7.26 亿美元。<br></p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/markets-news/denim/guess-inc-bested-wall-street-q2-eps-estimate-apparel-denim-jeans-fashion-retail-10514689/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Guess 第二季度收入超预期，股票大涨</b></a> | 由于欧洲市场表现强劲，截止至 7 月 30 日的三个月内，Guess 的利润上涨至 3230 万美元，去年同期则为 1830 万美元。华尔街预测其每股收益为 7 美分，猜测公司股价上涨了 15.1%。&nbsp;</p><p><a href=\"http://www.theindustrylondon.com/kate-spades-new-wearables-collection-launch-autumn/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Kate Spade 公布一组可穿戴产品，将于 11 月发售</b></a> | Kate Spade 的这组产品包括智能手表、手镯追踪器和有机硅追踪器（行动、睡眠等），由 Fossil 代工设计、开发、分销，价格在 125 至 250 美元之间。&nbsp;</p><p><b><a href=\"http://wwd.com/retail-news/direct-internet-catalogue/abercrombie-fitch-expansion-wholesale-zalando-fashion-teen-retail-apparel-10514310/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Abercrombie &amp; Fitch 入驻欧洲最大的时尚电商 Zalando</a></b> | Abercrombie &amp; Fitch 将把它的全线产品都放在 Zalando 上进行售卖，Zalando 则给 Abercrombie &amp; Fitch 带来了超过 1800 万顾客。Abercrombie &amp; Fitch 的主席 Fran Horowitz 认为，Zalando 是其进军欧洲市场的关键。&nbsp;</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-scoops/rihannas-fenty-puma-pop-up-bergdorf-goodman-six02-10514585/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Rihanna 的 Fenty 系列将不会出现在下个月的纽约时装周</b></a> | 9 月 6 日，Rihanna 与 Puma 合作的 Fenty 系列的秋冬新款在美国精品百货店 Bergdorf Goodman 和 Footlocker 的概念店 Six:02 开设 pop-up 店，但是，该系列将不会出席纽约时装周。&nbsp;</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p><a href=\"http://popbee.com/fashion/calvin-kleinzcashmere2016fw/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Calvin Klein 2016 秋冬 Cashmere </a>针织系列还不错。以黑色、石灰色、雪白色为主调，全部采用了意大利高级纱线制成。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160825084437Sk1MfCEBjqdvwmG0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160825084446Uk1yB3ciop69VjzW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160825084452iPNu4tZY8BAlvcpJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608250844526zvkEFQmP8uNZt3a.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>香港休闲服品牌 <a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/8/chocoolate-x-disney-pixar\" rel=\"nofollow\">:CHOCOOLATE 首次与 Disney </a>合作，推出了一系列色彩丰富的 Tee 及配饰。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608250845124ZzqPCp9T3BmaJce.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160825084512xF7189kzNib4opfa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160825084524devOCFpVYh95fwlQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160825084529yZAzBFnLQwpRmUOs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160825084534zT0KPBnuyHIkbRwq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160825084539M9kF0TGtporJymAv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>Fendi 与著名的珠宝设计师 Delfina Delettrez Fendi 合作，设计名为 <a href=\"http://popbee.com/accessories/watches/fendi-timepieces-policromia/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Policromia 的系列高级腕表</a>。全系列包括 20 款腕表，采用了孔雀石、青金石、绿色珍珠贝母等多重素材制成。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160825084550r7sNiUgnpOC0qRvj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160825084550nR4aDuATzwEdSCb6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160825084559TdnOBc8gVpPwokQ7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160825084559Q5Bcs87TNMXfyptw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>来自台湾的服装品牌<a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/8/wisdom-2016-autumn-winter-lazy-labor-collection\" rel=\"nofollow\"> wisdom 推出 2016 秋冬 lookbook</a>。该系列的主题为 Lazy Labor，强调衣服主体的轮廓和线条，以大面积的整体色块为主调，重新演绎城市休闲风格。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160825084612hnizbcyVBJEptgdZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160825084612hAfOHRKvyBTQairp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608250846125QduGcKFrP9NZeon.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608250846209uEq2XjVMRLQmyxB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160825084626GQmV3Ug9vuP2h6b8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>Adidas Originals 推出复古款式 80s Metal Toe 的新配色鞋款，大胆运用了金属和皮革这两种流行元素。鞋身由皮革制成，鞋头则以 bling bling 的金属碎石做装饰。Metal Toe 共有两种配色。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160825084640xh860mEgdynObRGJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160825084646fIYXlkBu5Sg3wEa1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160825084651oWcGiTRtvy04P1wO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160825084651ghtdUITVrun4cJO9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}